| ##############################################################################
| TEXAS INSTRUMENTS INCORPORATED
| Standard Linear and Logic Group
| IBIS Model of SN74LVC2G08
| DUAL 2-INPUT POSITIVE-AND GATE
| This file contains package information for the following:
|  SSOP 8-pin (DCT) package as [Component] LVC2G08_DCT
|  VSSOP 8-pin (DCU) package as [Component] LVC2G08_DCU
|  NanoStar WCSP 8-pin (YEA) package as [Component] LVC2G08_YEA
|  NanoFree WCSP 8-pin (YZA) package as [Component] LVC2G08_YZA
|  NanoStar WCSP 8-pin (YEP) package as [Component] LVC2G08_YEP
|  NanoFree WCSP 8-pin (YZP) package as [Component] LVC2G08_YZP
| This device can be powered at the following Vccs:
|  1.8 volt Vcc
|  2.5 volt Vcc
|  3.3 volt Vcc
|  5 volt Vcc
| This file provides unique models under the [Model Selector] for each Vcc.
| For operation at a specific Vcc, select the appropriate model after each
| [Model Selector] keyword.
|##############################################################################
|
[IBIS Ver]      3.2
[Comment char]  |_char
[File Name]     sn74lvc2g08.ibs
[File Rev]      1.2 | d_die
[Date]          June 29, 2004 
[Source]        Data created from TI-SPICE simulations at TI-SLL.
[Notes]         The following is an IBIS list for the LVC2G08.
                Please contact sllibis@ti.com with questions and
                comments concerning SLL IBIS models.
                - FILE REV HISTORY
                - 1.1 Release IBIS file on 09/11/02
                - 1.2 YEP and YZP packages released on 06/29/04
                - Due to the fact that the Device is 5.5-V Input tolarent, 
                  the pulldown model has some Non-Monotonic Warnings.
                - Power-clamp data has been deleted since there is no
                  power-clamp diode in the device.

